message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this incredible product! I think it's a game-changer, and I'm confident you'll love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $1,100,000. This is a great deal, considering the product's true value to you is $1,200,000. I'm willing to make a compromise to get this deal done, and I think you'll be thrilled with the value you'll get from this product.
